//Reflection// or //inversion// in a hypersphere with center $$c$$ and radius $$r$$ is the map

$$
x\mapsto c+\frac{r^2}{\|x-c\|^2}(x-c).
$$

If we consider $$\widehat\Bbb R^n\coloneqq\Bbb R^n\cup\{\infty\}$$ and map $$c$$ to $$\infty$$ and vice versa, this map is an [[involution|Involution]] of $$\widehat\Bbb R^n.$$